These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
There are 6 different nationalities: russian, brazilian, canadian, malaysian, french, australian
City: miami, boston, new-york, san-francisco, paris, berlin
 1. the canadian is in an odd position##4
 2. the australian is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
 3. the french is not the person traveling to paris##6
 4. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the brazilian##5
 5. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5
 6. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
 7. the person traveling to paris is not the brazilian##6
 8. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4
 9. the russian is somewhere between the person traveling to berlin and the malaysian##7
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
11. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
12. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
13. the person traveling to miami is the russian##1
14. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the french##5
15. the australian is the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | russian | canadian   | australian     | brazilian    | french   |
| City           | paris | miami   | berlin | san-francisco | new-york | boston |

