.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, 7up, sprite, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: volleyball, soccer, rowing, badminton, biathlon, skiing
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
 5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
 7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking lemonade is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is badminton##7
11. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
12. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
13. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
14. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
15. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
16. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
17. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking lemonade##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice | sprite | lemonade     | 7up      | almond-milk |
| Sport           | soccer         | rowing        | biathlon   | badminton | volleyball | skiing    |

