.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: taxi, van, motorbike, skateboard, car, jet-ski
6 different pets are kept: turtle, horse, cat, rat, chinchilla, goldfish
 1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
 3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 4. the owner of the horse is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 5. the person driving the taxi is not the owner of the turtle##6
 6. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 9. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
10. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the van##7
11. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
12. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
13. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
14. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Transport   | car        | skateboard | jet-ski    | taxi    | motorbike | van |
| Pet      | horse | chinchilla  | goldfish | rat | turtle | cat      |

