.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-4::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: july, november, april, june, october, march
City: hannover, nizza, marseilles, hamburg, san-francisco, edinburgh
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 3. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in october##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in march##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in june##7
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
13. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's birthday is in june##1
14. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Birthday      | june | november | march | april | october | july   |
| City   | marseilles  | hamburg      | hannover | san-francisco     | edinburgh | nizza |

