 2. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
12. the person who's birthday is in may is not the person who's hobby is dancing##6
13. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
14. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's birthday is in may##1

