.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-19::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: february, october, june, april, november, august
There are 6 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, cola, mirinda, milk, almond-milk
 1. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person drinking fanta##2
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 8. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
11. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person drinking soy-milk##7
13. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Birthday         | october   | november | february      | april | august  | june   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | almond-milk  | soy-milk | fanta   | milk | cola |

