.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
House: cape-cod, victorian, art-deco, futuristic, colonial, craftsman
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, february, july, november, may, september
 1. the colonial house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
 2. the art-deco house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 3. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 4. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in february##7
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 6. the art-deco house is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 7. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
10. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
11. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
12. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
13. the victorian house is somewhere between the cape-cod house and the art-deco house##7
14. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the colonial house##1
15. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| House   | art-deco         | futuristic | victorian | cape-cod   | craftsman | colonial  |
| Birthday     | may | november  | july  | september | february  | june |

 